Xuelin Road (simplified Chinese: 学林路; traditional Chinese: 學林路; pinyin: Xuélín Lù) is a station on Line 13 of the Shanghai Metro, part of phase three of the line.  Located at Zhongke Road and Gebaini Road in Pudong, Shanghai, the station opened with the phases 2 and 3 extensions of Line 13 on 30 December 2018.